      { question: "How far is Amritsar from Delhi?", answer: "Amritsar is 450 km from Delhi, about 7-8 hours by car via NH44. We offer Delhi-Amritsar cab packages. Alternatively, there are frequent flights (1 hour) and trains (6-8 hours)." }
